headline: Guggenheim Initiates Equinix (EQIX) with “Buy” and $933 Price Target
summary: Equinix, Inc. (NASDAQ:EQIX) is one of Goldman Sachs’ top REIT stock picks. On July 9, Guggenheim initiated coverage on Equinix, assigning a “Buy” rating with a price target of $933. The firm identified Equinix as one of the two very large publicly traded data center operators benefiting from its scale in capital access and technology […]

headline: VNQ: Data Centers Are Carrying Commercial Real Estate
summary: VNQ offers diversified exposure to commercial real estate, focusing on blue-chip REITs with a low expense ratio, making it attractive for thematic investors.
